name: Handmade
description:
This is a digital collage series I made, based on my own dream. 

* ✧･ﾟ: ✧･I Had a dream last night.･ﾟ✧:･ﾟ✧ * 
In that dream I was in a big houses. They had pool, music and drinks. It was late at night. It was an internal party. Some dancing, some swimming, and I was there on the barbecue section. There was sausages, meats and many others. I start to pick a big knife and cut my own right hand using my left. I feel no pain, but blood was everywhere. Then I start to cook my own hand single-handedly.
